1. Moj posao zahteva različite *radnje* tokom dana. (My job requires different *actions* during the day.)
2. Sva *radnja* u gradu stala je zbog kiše. (All the *activity* in the city stopped because of the rain.)
3. Molim te, završi tu *radnju* što pre. (Please finish that *task* as soon as possible.)
4. U ovoj *radnji* možete kupiti sve vrste voća i povrća. (In this *shop* you can buy all kinds of fruit and vegetables.)
5. Vlada je donela novu *radnju* o zaštiti životne sredine. (The government has passed a new *measure* on environmental protection.)
6. Nisam siguran da li će ta *radnja* biti uspešna. (I'm not sure if that *action* will be successful.)
7. Bez obzira na sve *radnje*, nismo uspeli da završimo projekat na vreme. (Despite all the *efforts*, we failed to complete the project on time.)
8. *Radnje* koje si preduzeo su bile veoma hrabre. (The *actions* you took were very brave.)
9. Ova *radnja* me podseća na jednu situaciju iz prošlosti. (This *scenario* reminds me of a situation from the past.)
10. Svakodnevne *radnje* čine život zanimljivim. (Everyday *activities* make life interesting.)